20years%20and%20the%20harrowing%20struggle%20had%20led%20to%20depression.%20The%20cops%20had%20said%20that%20the%20family%20had%20told%20them%20that%20the%20cancer%20fight%20may%20have%20pushed%20him%20to%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Singh%20has%20trashed%20these%20claims%20in%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20and%20said%20that%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsurvivor%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20his%20cancer%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20life-threatening%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHe%20got%20my%20father-in-law%20and%20my%20sister-in-law%20treated.%20His%20cancer%20was%20not%20life-threatening%2C%20never.%20He%20was%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20at%20work.%20Maybe%20his%20department%20colleagues%20would%20know%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%2C%2059%2C%20was%20a%20deputy%20commissioner%20in%20the%20GST%20department%20in%20Ghaziabad.%20He%20jumped%20to%20death%20from%20his%2014th-floor%20flat%20at%20Apex%20Athena%2C%20a%20residential%20complex%20in%20Noida's%20Sector%2075%2C%20around%2011%20am%20yesterday.%20He%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20sons.%20His%20elder%20son%20works%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20the%20younger%20son%20is%20a%20dentistry%20student%20at%20Sharda%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20not%20fear%20anything%20like%20this.%20This%20is%20not%20normal.%20He%20became%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20system.%20If%20anyone%20can%20answer%20these%20questions%2C%20they%20can%20speak%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Singh%20also%20rubbished%20reports%20that%20said%20her%20husband's%20prostrate%20cancer%20had%20advanced%20to%20the%20last%20stage.%20%26quot%3BMay%20God%20forgive%20them.%20I%20cannot%20silence%20everyone.%20My%20husband%20was%20not%20a%20fourth-stage%20cancer%20patient%20and%20I%20have%20proof%20of%20this.%20Whatever%20has%20happened%2C%20the%20system%20is%20responsible.%20This%20must%20be%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2F