rgest%20single-day%20drops%20in%20Tesla%20shares%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20fine%20long-term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Look%20At%20Tesla%20Shares%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20shares%20plunged%2015.4%20per%20cent%20by%20the%20end%20of%20Monday's%20trading%20session.%20It%20was%20the%20largest%20single-day%20percentage%20decline%20since%20September%202020%2C%20when%20shares%20saw%20a%20decline%20of%20over%2021%20per%20cent%20in%20a%20single%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Tesla%20stocks%20witnessed%20a%20total%20decline%20of%2041.4%20per%20cent%20year-to-date%20so%20far%20in%202025.%20This%20includes%20a%20drop%20of%20over%2036.6%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20past%20months.%20As%20of%20March%2010%2C%20Tesla%20stock%20has%20fallen%20by%20more%20than%20half%20to%20a%20new%20market%20cap%20of%20%24696%20billion%20after%20reaching%20its%20all-time%20largest%20market%20capitalization%20of%20%241.5%20trillion%20on%20December%2017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUBS%20has%20also%20lowered%20its%20price%20target%20on%20the%20stock%20to%20%24225%20from%20%24259%2C%20citing%20lower%20delivery%20forecasts%20for%20the%20first%20quarter%20it%20sees%20resulting%20from%20softer%20demand%20for%20Tesla's%20Model%203%20and%20Model%20Y%20vehicles.%20This%20contributed%20to%20the%20sell-off%2C%20along%20with%20broader%20concerns%20about%20the%20US%20economy%20facing%20a%20recession%20and%20a%20widening%20trade%20war%20amid%20President%20Trump's%20tariff%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20ended%20the%20trading%20day%202.7%20per%20cent%20lower--its%20lowest%20closing%20level%20since%20September%20and%20its%20biggest%20daily%20percentage%20decline%20since%20December.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20dropped%202%20per%20cent%2C%20for%20its%20lowest%20close%20since%20November%204%2C%20the%20day%20before%20Mr%20Trump's%20election%20as%20President.