nce%20December.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20dropped%202%20per%20cent%2C%20for%20its%20lowest%20close%20since%20November%204%2C%20the%20day%20before%20Trump's%20election%20as%20President.%20The%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20plunged%204%20per%20cent%20to%20a%20near%20six-month%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nasdaq%20confirmed%20a%20correction%20last%20week%2C%20having%20tumbled%20more%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20from%20its%20December%20all-time%20high.%20MSCI's%20global%20stock%20index%20also%20fell%20more%20than%202%20per%20cent%20for%20its%20biggest%20one-day%20drop%2C%20touching%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20January%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Trump's%20aid%20Elon%20Musk's%20Tesla%20saw%20a%20decline%20of%20about%2015.4%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20chip%20giant%20Nvidia%20was%20down%20more%20than%205%20per%20cent.%20Other%20major%20tech%20stocks%20including%20Meta%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Alphabet%20also%20saw%20a%20steep%20plunge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20trade%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Japan's%20Nikkei%20225%20was%20down%202.5%20per%20cent%2C%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%20was%202.3%20per%20cent%20lower%20and%20Australia's%20S%26amp%3BP%2FASX%20200%20was%20off%20by%201.8%20per%20cent.%20Indian%20equities%20opened%20lower%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20tracking%20a%20broad%20sell-off%20across%20Asian%20markets%20after%20Wall%20Street%20tumbled%20overnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nifty%2050%20fell%200.51%20per%20cent%20to%2022%2C345.95%20as%20of%209%3A15%20a.m.%20IST%20while%20the%20Sensex%20lost%200.5%20per%20cent%20to%2073%2C743.88.%20Nifty%2050%20is%20trading%20about%2014.5%25%20below%20the%20all-time%20high%20hit%20in%20September%202024%2C%20hurt%20by%20slowing%20earnings%20growth%2C%20US%20tariff%20uncertainty%20and%20relentless%20foreign%20selling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20pan-European%20STOXX%20600%20index%20had%20ended%20down%201.29%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fixed%20income%2C%20yields%20fell%20with%20US%20government%20bonds%20in%20demand%20after%20the%20Trump%20interview%20cut%20into%20investor%20confidence.%20The%202-year%20note%20yield%2C%20which%20typically%20moves%20in%20step%20with%20interest%20rate%20expectations%20for%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20fell%2010.4%20basis%20points%20to%203.898%20per%20cent%2C%20from%204.002%20per%20cent%20late%20on%20Friday%2C%20on%20track%20for%20their%20largest%20daily%20drop%20since%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yield%20on%20benchmark%20US%2010-year%20notes%20fell%209.3%20basis%20points%20to%204.225%20per%20cent%20while%20the%2030-year%20bond%20yield%20fell%206.9%20basis%20points%20to%204.548%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20currencies%2C%20investors%20looked%20for%20safety.%20Against%20the%20Japanese%20yen%2C%20the%20dollar%20weakened%200.5%20per%20cent%20to%20147.29.%20However%2C%20the%20euro%20was%20down%200.06%20per%20cent%20at%20%241.0826%20and%20Sterling%20weakened%200.45%20per%20cent%20to%20%241.2862.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20also%20sank%20as%20tariff%20uncertainty%20kept%20investors%20on%20edge%20along%20with%20rising%20output%20from%20OPEC%2B%20producers%2C%20although%20potential%20sanctions%20on%20Iranian%20oil%20exports%20limited%20losses.%20American%20crude%20settled%20down%201.51%20per%20cent%20or%20%241.01%20at%20%2466.03%20a%20barrel%20while%20Brent%20settled%20at%20%2469.28%20per%20barrel%2C%20down%20%241.08%20or%201.53%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20prices%20also%20plunged%20as%20profit-taking%20countered%20support%20from%20safe-haven%20demand%20fueled%20by%20geopolitical%20uncertainty%2C%20with%20focus%20on%20the%20US%20inflation%20data%20later%20this%20week.%20Spot%20gold%20fell%200.86%20per%20cent%20to%20%242%2C885.63%20an%20ounce.%20US%20gold%20futures%20fell%200.76%20per%20cent%20to%20%242%2C882.70%20an%20ounce.%20Copper%20declined%201.25%20per%20cent%20to%20%249%2C493.00%20a%20tonne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20bitcoin%20fell%204.88%20per%20cent%20to%20%2479%2C028.58%20after%20touching%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Fox%20News%20on%20Sunday%2C%20President%20Trump%20appeared%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20recession%20concerns.%20When%20asked%20about%20it%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hate%20to%20predict%20things%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20period%20of%20transition%20because%20what%20we're%20doing%20is%20very%20big.%20We're%20bringing%20wealth%20back%20to%20America.%20That's%20a%20big%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20trading%20at%20Wall%20Street%20closed%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20White%20House%20official%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20a%20strong%20divergence%20between%20%5Bthe%5D%20animal%20spirits%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20what%20we're%20actually%20seeing%20unfold%20from%20businesses%20and%20business%20leaders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20latter%20is%20obviously%20more%20meaningful%20than%20the%20former%20on%20what's%20in%20store%20for%20the%20economy%20in%20the%20medium%20to%20long%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20did%20not%20appear%20on%20camera%20on%20Monday%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rarity%20for%20the%20commander%20in%20chief%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20US%20stock%20market%20plunged%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvestors%20Seek%20Safety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20had%20started%20seeking%20safety%20following%20President%20Trump's%20remarks%2C%20with%20market%20strategists%20pointing%20to%20the%20comments%20as%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20Monday's%20cautious%20mood%20among%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20administration%20seems%20a%20little%20more%20accepting%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20they're%20OK%20with%20the%20market%20falling%2C%20and%20they're%20potentially%20even%20OK%20with%20a%20recession%20in%20order%20to%20exact%20their%20broader%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20Mayfield%2C%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Baird%20in%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20a%20big%20wake-up%20call%20for%20Wall%20Street.%20There%20had%20been%20a%20sense%20that%20President%20Trump%20kind%20of%20measured%20his%20success%20on%20stock%20market%20performance.%20There%20was%20even%20somewhat%20of%20a%20'Trump%20put'%20so%20to%20speak.%20And%20I%20think%20we're%20seeing%20that's%20not%20the%20case%2C%20so%20the%20market%20is%20starting%20to%20reflect%20that%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20occupant%20in%20the%20White%20House%20is%20himself%20not%20terribly%20optimistic%20about%20short-term%20growth%20expectations%2C%20why%20should%20the%20market%20be%20optimistic%20about%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Will%20Compernolle%2C%20macro%20strategist%20at%20FHN%20Financial.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741670340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fsl5f0ei_markets-afp_625x300_11_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-sell-off-hits-wall-street-as-trump-policies-spark-recession-fears-7895963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Share%20markets%20across%20the%20globe%20witnessed%20sharp%20losses%20after%20a%20selloff%20in%20America%2C%20triggered%20by%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Monday%20refusing%20to%20rule%20out%20the%20suggestion%20that%20his%20tariffs%20could%20trigger%20a%20recession%20in%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmassive-sell-off-hits-wall-street-as-trump-policies-spark-recession-fears-7895963%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Complaint%20filed%20against%20Thalapath