iding%20for%20cooperation%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20capacity%20building%2C%20trade%20and%20tackling%20cross-border%20financial%20crimes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20contingent%20of%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20island%20nation's%2057th%20national%20day%20celebrations%20on%20Wednesday%20along%20with%20a%20warship%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20the%20Akash%20Ganga%20skydiving%20team%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20leaving%20for%20Mauritius%2C%20PM%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20that%20his%20visit%20would%20open%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20and%20bright%26quot%3B%20chapter%20in%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20In%20his%20departure%20statement%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20he%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20engaging%20with%20the%20leadership%20of%20Mauritius%20to%20elevate%20%26quot%3Bour%20partnership%20in%20all%20its%20facets%20and%20strengthen%20our%20enduring%20friendship%20for%20the%20progress%20and%20prosperity%20of%20our%20peoples%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BMauritius%20is%20a%20close%20maritime%20neighbour%2C%20a%20key%20partner%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20and%20a%20gateway%20to%20the%20African%20Continent.%20We%20are%20connected%20by%20history%2C%20geography%20and%20culture...Deep%20mutual%20trust%2C%20a%20shared%20belief%20in%20the%20values%20of%20democracy%2C%20and%20celebration%20of%20our%20diversity%20are%20our%20strengths%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20close%20and%20historical%20people-to-people%20connection%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20is%20a%20source%20of%20shared%20pride.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDuring%20his%20two-day%20stay%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20call%20on%20the%20president%20of%20Mauritius%2C%20meet%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20and%20hold%20meetings%20with%20senior%20dignitaries%20and%20leaders%20of%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20island%20nation.%20He%20will%20also%20interact%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%2C%20and%20inaugurate%20the%20civil%20service%20college%20and%20the%20area%20health%20centre%2C%20both%20built%20with%20India's%20grant%20assistance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry%2C%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20Mauritius%20authorities%20will%20sign%20a%20technical%20agreement%20on%20exchanging%20information%20on%20white%20shipping%20during%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit.%20The%20two%20sides%20will%20also%20sign%20several%20agreements%20in%20the%20field%20of%20capacity%20building%2C%20bilateral%20trade%2C%20tackling%20cross-border%20financial%20crimes%20and%20promoting%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Centre%20for%20Ocean%20Information%20Services%20and%20the%20Mauritius%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20will%20sign%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20(MoU)%20to%20create%20a%20framework%20for%20cooperating%20in%20maritime%20zone%20management%20and%20ocean%20observation%20and%20research.%20India's%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20and%20the%20Financial%20Crime%20Commission%20of%20Mauritius%20will%20also%20sign%20an%20MoU%20on%20combating%20financial%20crimes.%20The%20pact%20is%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20cooperation%20in%20intelligence%20and%20technical%20assistance%20to%20combat%20money%20laundering%20and%20related%20crimes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20earlier%20visited%20Mauritius%20in%202015%20and%201998.%20The%20official%20account%20of%20Modi%20Archive%20shared%20a%20glimpse%20of%20his%20October%201998%20visit%20to%20%26quot%3BMini%20India%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20BJP%20National%20General%20Secretary%20to%20address%20the%20International%20Ramayana%20Conference%20in%20Moka.%20During%20his%202015%20tour%20as%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20had%20announced%20SAGAR%20(Security%20and%20Growth%20for%20All%20in%20the%20Region)%2C%20India's%20doctrine%20of%20maritime%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20is%20amongst%20the%20largest%20trading%20partners%20of%20Mauritius%2C%20a%20former%20British%20and%20French%20colony%20that%20gained%20independence%20in%201968.%C2%A0A%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20special%20ties%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20Indian-origin%20people%20comprise%20nearly%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20island%20nation's%20population%20of%201.2%20million%20(12%20lakhs).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%2C%20India%20on%20Saturday%20said%20it%20supports%20the%20island%20nation%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20reach%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20deal%20with%20the%20UK%20over%20the%20Chagos%20Islands%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20The%20issue%20is%20expected%20to%20figure%20in%20Mr%20Modi's%20talks%20with%20Mauritian%20Prime%20Minister%20Ramgoolam.%20In%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20UK%20announced%20its%20decision%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20Chagos%20Islands%20to%20Mauritius%20after%20more%20than%20half%20a%20century%20under%20a%20historic%20agreement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741665180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8i527eeo_modi-pti_625x300_11_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmodi-mauritius-visit-pm-narendra-modi-lands-in-port-louis-for-2-day-visit-gets-warm-welcome-from-mauritius-counterpart-navin-ramgoolam-at-airport-7896346%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20landed%20on%20Port%20Louis%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20a%20two-day%20state%20visit%20to%20Mauritius%2C%20during%20which%20he%20will%20attend%20the%20island%20nation's%2057th%20national%20day%20celebrations%20as%20the%20guest%20of%20honour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmodi-mauritius-visit-pm-narendra-modi-lands-in-port-louis-for-2-day-visit-gets-warm-welcome-from-mauritius-counterpa