3EThe%20valuation%20multiple%20decline%20makes%20Nvidia%20cheaper%20today%20than%20it%20was%20when%20ChatGPT%20was%20first%20released%20on%20November%2030%2C%202022.%20The%20stock%20is%20trading%20at%20its%20cheapest%20level%20since%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Reitzes%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Melius%20Research%2C%20said%20the%20valuation%20dynamic%20for%20Nvidia%20also%20holds%20true%20on%20a%20forward%20P%2FE%20ratio%2C%20which%20incorporates%20Wall%20Street's%20year-ahead%20earnings%20estimates%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reitzes%2C%20with%20a%20forward%20P%2FE%20ratio%20of%2024%20times%2C%20Nvidia%20stock%20is%2041%25%20cheaper%20than%20it%20was%20when%20ChatGPT%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nvidia%20valuations%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf38fc585f1dff88b1affb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMelius%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20impressive%20feat%20given%20that%20Nvidia%20shares%20have%20soared%20583%25%20since%20OpenAI%20released%20ChatGPT%20to%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20stock-price%20surge%20was%20backed%20up%20by%20profits%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20GPU%20business%20boomed%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20strong%20demand%20from%20AI%20companies.%20Nvidia's%20net%20income%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202025%20soared%20788%25%20compared%20to%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023%2C%20which%20ended%20in%20January%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReitzes%20believes%20there's%20a%20valuation%20disconnect%20and%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20risks%20have%20largely%20priced%20into%20semiconductor%20stocks%20like%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20very%20optimistic%2C%26quot%3B%20Reitzes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20optimism%20stems%20from%20Nvidia's%20GPU%20Technology%20Conference%20next%20week%2C%20where%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20is%20expected%20to%20assure%20investors%20that%20the%20AI%20boom%20remains%20alive%20and%20well%20and%20unveil%20its%20product%20roadmap%20into%202027%2C%20according%20to%20Reitzes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20Reitzes%20is%20staying%20bullish%20on%20Nvidia%20is%20because%20he's%20seen%20this%20valuation%20compression%20play%20out%20before%20in%20shares%20of%20a%20technology%20stalwart%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Faapl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20similar%20thing%20happened%20to%20Apple%20actually%20a%20long%20time%20ago%2C%20when%20its%20forward%20multiple%20went%20from%2033%20times%20on%20the%20day%20it%20announced%20the%20iPhone%20in%202008%20and%20shrank%20to%2015%20times%20by%20the%20end%20of%202008%20in%20the%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Reitzes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20know%2C%20the%20mobile%20trend%20didn't%20end%20then%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Apple%20now%20trades%20at%2031x%20earnings%20on%20much%20larger%20numbers.%20If%20Nvidia%20duplicates%20its%20own%20version%20of%20this%20industry%20stewardship%2C%20we%20could%20look%20back%20at%20this%20period%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20have%20a%20good%20chuckle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelius%20Research%20rates%20Nvidia%20at%20%26quot%3BBuy%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20%24170%20price%20target%2C%20representing%20potential%20upside%20of%2060%25%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-correction-plunges-valuation-metric-levels-before-chatgpt-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741638730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6747863e9f2901eb60377685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%