%26quot%3B%20feature%20that%20automatically%20adjusts%20the%20firmness%20as%20you%20move%20around%20at%20night.%20This%20is%20ideal%20since%20I%20often%20switch%20between%20side%20and%20stomach%20sleeping.%20Since%20the%20comfort%20adjusts%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20choose%20and%20stick%20with%20a%20position.%20Also%2C%20the%20mattress%20tracks%20your%20sleep%20quality%20and%20offers%20personalized%20insights%20for%20improved%20sleep%20through%20the%20SleepIQ%20app.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94James%20Brains%2C%20senior%20reporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESoothingly%20scented%20incense%20sticks%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20nag%20champa%20incense%20sticks%20on%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5af45d89fe3eea2b008b45fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThough%20you%20need%20to%20be%20careful%2C%20incense%20has%20been%20used%20to%20create%20a%20calming%20atmosphere%20for%20centuries.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENag%20Champa%20Incense%20Sticks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sensitive%20to%20odors%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20different%20scents%20can%20wake%20me%20up.%20This%20is%20great%20for%20avoiding%20disaster%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20fire%20but%20not%20helpful%20when%20my%20kid%20decides%20to%20cook%20at%20two%20in%20the%20morning.%20I've%20found%20incense%20does%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20masking%20odors%2C%20so%20I%20can%20go%20back%20to%20sleep%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20put%20me%20in%20a%20calm%20mood%20to%20fall%20asleep%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20tried%20almost%20every%20Satya%20variety%20in%20my%20decades%20of%20burning%20incense%2C%20and%20my%20favorites%20are%20Nag%20Champa%20and%20Romance.%20I%20recommend%20starting%20with%20a%20variety%20pack%20to%20find%20your%20favorite.%20Also%2C%20be%20extra%20careful%20using%20incense%20as%20it%20can%20start%20a%20fire.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20James%20Brains%2C%20senior%20reporter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20convenient%20pillow%20spray%20you%20can%20bring%20anywhere%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20box%20and%20bottle%20of%20thisworks%20pillow%20spray%20on%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5af45e3b4c9ab969008b46d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20Works%20Deep%20Pillow%20Spray's%20combination%20of%20chamomile%2C%20vetivert%2C%20and%20lavender%20brings%20calmness%20to%20your%20sleep%20routine.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20Works%20Deep%20Pillow%20Spray%2C%2075ml%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lent%20this%20spray%20out%20to%20friends%2C%20roommates%2C%20and%20family%20to%20help%20them%20sleep%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20had%20trouble%20getting%20it%20%3Cem%3Eback%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20them.%20The%20power%20blend%20of%20lavender%2C%20vetivert%2C%20and%20chamomile%20is%20unbelievably%20soothing%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20set%20up%20a%20sleep%20routine%20for%20me%20that%20signifies%20to%20my%20body%20it's%20time%20to%20relax.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20Mara%20Leighton%2C%20former%20senior%20reporter%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20travel%20pillow%20so%20you%20can%20finally%20fall%20asleep%20on%20your%20flight%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sleeps%20on%20a%20plane%20wearing%20the%20trtl%20travel%20pillow%20around%20her%20neck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d8bd3d92e22af44cf56fb37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Trtl%20Pillow%20is%20a%20must-have%20for%20getting%20rest%20while%20traveling.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrtl%20Pillow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-travel-pillow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Trtl%20pillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20looks%20nothing%20like%20a%20pillow.%20It%20seems%20more%20like%20a%20scarf%20or%20blanket%2C%20and%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20that's%20actually%20what%20it%20is.%20A%20soft%2C%20lightweight%20fleece%20wrap%20hides%20and%20cushions%20a%20plastic%20neck%20support%20on%20one%20side%2C%20which%20rests%20on%20either%20your%20shoulder%20or%20your%20chest%20to%20keep%20your%20head%20in%20a%20comfortable%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20neck%20support%20consists%20of%20a%20few%20stiff%20ribs%20on%20one%20end%20of%20the%20scarf.%20To%20use%20the%20Trtl%2C%20simply%20place%20the%20ribs%20in%20the%20position%20you%20find%20most%20comfortable%2C%20then%20wrap%20the%20scarf%20around%20your%20neck.%20Velcro%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20ribs%20holds%20the%20wrap%20in%20place%20while%20you%20doze%20off.%20The%20ribs%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20flexibility%20to%20eliminate%20any%20pressure%20points%20or%20discomfort.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20David%20Slotnick%2C%20contributor%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20light%20that%20slowly%20dims%20at%20night%20and%20brightens%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20mimic%20a%20sunrise%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20casper%20glow%20light%20sits%20on%20a%20night%20table%20near%20a%20book%20and%20pair%20of%20glasses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e5574e9fee23d3f174b0175%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Casper%20Glow%20Light%20helps%20you%20unwind%20at%20night%20and%20get%20going%20in%20the%20morning%20using%20light.%3Cp%3ECasper%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECasper%20Glow%20Light%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20circadian%20