22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20ensured%20that%20%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EAnganwadi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20centres%20opened%20on%20time%20and%20were%20habitable%20enough%20for%20kids%20to%20come%20daily.%20%E2%80%9COur%20interventions%20would%20not%20have%20been%20effective%20if%20children%20did%20not%20come%20to%20these%20centres.%20So%2C%20we%20renovated%202%2C200%20%3Cem%3EAnganwadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20centres%20and%20built%20600%20new%20centres%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20in%20rented%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20nutritional%20absorption%20capacity%2C%20the%20district%20started%20providing%20daily%20iron%20and%20multivitamin%20supplementation%20as%20part%20of%20its%20extensive%20nutritional%20supplementation%20programme%2C%20%E2%80%98Abhinav%20Pehel%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20initially%20started%20by%20Himanshu%E2%80%99s%20predecessor%2C%20Abhishek%20Goyal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20millet-based%20supplements%20and%20plant-produced%20fortified%20foods%20also%20ensured%20a%20nutritious%20boost%20for%20both%20children%20and%20mothers.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20the%20malnourished%20children%20were%20given%20millet%20bars%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F306747%2Fkirti-yadav-kukclean-bengaluru-offers-plant-based-vegan-sugar-free-healthy-snacks-for-diabetes-patients%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eragi%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnganwadis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20improving%20attendance%20and%20retention.%20Earlier%2C%20only%20%3Cem%3Edaal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pulses)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grams)%2C%20refined%20o