es%2C%20where%20we%20inform%20them%20about%20CybageKhushboo.%20Every%20year%2C%20they%20receive%20applications%20and%20send%20us%20the%20ones%20they%20feel%20fit%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20scholarships%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ritu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20CybageKhushboo%20has%20formed%20partnerships%20with%2019%20colleges%2C%20and%20the%20team%20continues%20to%20add%20more%20institutions%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ritu%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CEducation%20is%20not%20just%20about%20textbooks.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20building%20character%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20world.%20Through%20CybageKhushboo%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20achieve%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Cybage%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741349454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FCK_1_11zon-1741342203.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D412059%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Talent%20is%20everywhere%2C%20but%20opportunity%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%94%20CybageKhushboo%20is%20changing%20that.%20Through%20scholarships%2C%20career%20training%2C%20and%20mentorship%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20bridging%20the%20gap%20for%20underprivileged%20students%2C%20helping%20them%20land%20jobs%20at%20leading%20companies%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Bajaj%20Finserv.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A161%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412059%2Fcybagekhushboo-scholarship-holistic-development-of-students-land-high-paying-jobs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20High-Demand%20Crop%20Is%20Helping%20Farmers%20Earn%20Up%20to%20Rs%20800%2FKg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20moringa%2C%20or%20the%20drumstick%20tree%2C%20evokes%20memories%20of%20mothers%20lovingly%20adding%